     configuration, database schemas and migrations, edge functions, scripts,
     documentation, diagrams, designs, logos owned by Licensor, build tooling,
     and any updates, patches, or derivative works thereof.

1.2  “Licensee” means any individual or entity authorized by Licensor to access
     or use the Software, including employees, contractors, and affiliated
     operating entities (including Bishnupriya Fuels).

1.3  “Authorized User” means a natural person granted credentials by Licensee
     or Licensor to use the Software in the ordinary course of internal operations.

1.4  “Confidential Information” means the Software and all non-public technical,
     business, operational, financial, or customer information disclosed in
     connection with the Software, whether in written, electronic, or oral form.

1.5  “Production Data” means live business data processed by the Software,
     including sales, meter readings, credit ledgers, invoices, payroll-related
     records, and backups thereof.


