7.3  Production Data and customer/staff personal data processed via the Software
     shall be handled in accordance with applicable Indian law (including the
     Information Technology Act, 2000 and the Digital Personal Data Protection
     Act, 2023, as applicable) and Licensor’s internal policies.

7.4  Licensee shall not exfiltrate, sell, or misuse Production Data. Backups and
     exports (including Google Drive backups) may be created only through
     approved procedures and stored only in approved locations.

7.5  Upon request or termination, Licensee shall return or securely destroy
     Confidential Information and Production Data in its possession, except where
     retention is required by law (in which case such materials remain subject to
     confidentiality).


